<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>비밀번호 찾기:studyTight</title>
    <style>
        @import url(/public/login/login.css);
        @import url(/public/font.css); 
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="warp">
        <div class="login_header"> 
            <div class ="logo_area"> 
                <img src="/public/media/logo_big.png" onclick="location.href='/'">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <!-- 여기는 본문 들어갈 메인 섹션 -->
            <div class="login">
                <form id="findpw-form" action="/email/findpw" method="POST">
                    <div class="login_section">
                        <h2 style="margin: auto 0; text-align: center;" >비밀번호 초기화 이메일 전송 성공</h2>
                        <div style="text-align: center;">비밀번호 초기화 이메일 전송을 성공했습니다.&emsp;전송된 이메일을 확인해주세요.</div>
                        <br>
                        <div class="login_form">
                            <input type="text" name="email" id="email" placeholder="이메일 입력" required autofocus/>
                        </div>
                        <input type="submit" title="비밀번호 초기화 메일 발송" value="비밀번호 초기화 메일 발송" class="login_btn">
                        <div class="login_info">
                            <a target="_self" href="/" class="find_password">로그인</a>
                            <span class="bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <a target="_self" href="/signup/agree" class="register">회원가입</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>